post:
 
			
			@chosenjade   
Thank you for the update and information regarding Teoh's. It is good to know that Uncle and Auntie Teoh are well and have decided to retire. We just moved to Switzerland 6 weeks ago and were wrapped when we found Teoh's restaurant. We felt so lost last night when we saw the restaurant vacated. Your description of them is spot on - Uncle Teoh gave us his clock parking card 4 weeks ago and taught us how to use it as we had no idea.   
Please wish them well and thank them for our two unforgettable dinners.
